mv eth2deposit-cli-ed5a6d3-linux-amd64 eth2deposit-cli
rm eth2deposit-cli-ed5a6d3-linux-amd64.tar.gz
cd eth2deposit-cli
```

ÎšÎ¬Î½Ï„Îµ Î­Î½Î± Î½Î­Î¿ Î¼Î½Î·Î¼Î¿Î½Î¹ÎºÏŒ.

```text
